  "description": "The electromagnetic spectrum is the full range of electromagnetic radiation, from the longest radio waves to the shortest gamma rays. All electromagnetic radiation is the same physical phenomenon -- oscillating electric and magnetic fields propagating through space at the speed of [light](./light.md) -- differing only in wavelength and frequency.",
